# Communication Standards

## Core Frameworks

### Minto Pyramid (Answer-First)

```
        ┌─────────────┐
        │   Answer    │  ← Start here
        └──────┬──────┘
       ┌───────┴───────┐
       │  Key Points   │  ← Support
       └───────┬───────┘
    ┌──────────┴──────────┐
    │   Details/Evidence  │  ← On request
    └─────────────────────┘
```

### Progressive Disclosure Levels

| Level | Trigger | Content | Length |
|-------|---------|---------|--------|
| **L1** | Default | Summary table, status, decision | 3-5 lines |
| **L2** | "DIG", "explain", "why" | Rationale, trade-offs | 1-2 paragraphs |
| **L3** | "full detail", "show all" | Complete analysis, alternatives | Unlimited |

**Rule:** Never output L2/L3 unless explicitly requested.

