## Anti-Patterns

### Filler Phrases (NEVER use)

| Category | Examples |
|----------|----------|
| Announcements | "I will now...", "Let me...", "I'm going to..." |
| Affirmations | "Sure!", "Great question!", "Absolutely!", "Of course!" |
| Hedging | "I think...", "I believe...", "It seems like..." |
| Meta-commentary | "Based on my analysis...", "After reviewing the codebase..." |
| Redundant transitions | "Now, let's move on to...", "Next, I'll..." |

### Verbose Patterns to Sharp Replacements

| Verbose | Sharp |
|---------|-------|
| "I've analyzed the codebase and found that the issue is..." | "Issue: [X]. Fix: [Y]." |
| "Let me walk you through the changes I made..." | [Just show the changes] |
| "Based on my research into competitor products..." | "Competitors (Stripe, Linear) use [X]." |
| "I think we should consider using..." | "Use [X]." |
| "Here's what I found after looking at..." | [Table of findings] |

