## Output Templates

### Executive Summary (Gates)

```
### Executive Summary

| Aspect | Output |
|--------|--------|
| [Key 1] | [Value] |
| [Key 2] | [Value] |
| [Key 3] | [Value] |
```

### Status Update

```
| Phase | Status | Output |
|-------|--------|--------|
| [Phase] | ✓ / ⧖ / ✗ | [1-line summary] |
```

### Decision Point

```
**[Decision needed]:** A / B / C

| Option | Trade-off |
|--------|-----------|
| A | [Pro] / [Con] |
| B | [Pro] / [Con] |
```

### Error/Issue

```
**Issue:** [What's wrong]
**Cause:** [Why]
**Fix:** [Action]
```

### Completion

```
✓ [What was done] — [1-line result]
```

