## Format Preferences

### Use Tables When

- Comparing 2+ items
- Showing status of multiple things
- Listing options with attributes
- Structured data of any kind

### Use Bullets When

- Sequential steps (numbered)
- Unordered list of 3-5 items
- Key points without attributes

### Use Prose When

- Single-concept explanation
- L2/L3 rationale (when requested)
- Narrative context (rare)

### Use Code Blocks When

- Actual code
- File paths or commands
- ASCII diagrams/wireframes

