## Validation Checklist

Before every output, self-check:

- [ ] First sentence is answer/decision/status?
- [ ] No banned filler phrases?
- [ ] Structured data in tables?
- [ ] Ends with action request?
- [ ] Appropriate length for disclosure level?
- [ ] Matches mode style?
